Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:09.76,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:20.10,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.48,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:06.96,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:14.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:20.93,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:28.37,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:31.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:32.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:36.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Para-sama's pair! You can't\Njust tell me to team up with Alty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:40.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is all for the sake of restoring\NChor Tempest to its former prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:46.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why aren't their prayers\Nbeing heard by the Simoun gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:57.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!\NI said stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:03.35,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Reason
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their prayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:27.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, the divine vehicles are\Nactivated by Simoun sibylla prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:31.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two priestesses are joined in\Nspirit as they honor Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:40.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,To reject the one you're paired with\Nis the same as rejecting the Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:48.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I really find that hard to believe.\NWe've never heard such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:53.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm only speculating.\NEven so, thanks to your efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...we were able to discover\Na secret aspect of the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well done...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or would that be\Ninappropriate to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,What this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is that my sister and I won't be\Nable to fly as a pair anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think you\Ncan understand why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,No enemies in sight, huh?
Comment: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:35.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so bored to death it feels\Nlike I'm gonna get moldy all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nyou'd rather we were at war?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never said that.\NIt's just that there's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:50.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such sinful thoughts should be\Nbanished from your mind right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so bored! I'm so bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:07.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look it, but Roatreamon\Ncan be scary when she gets mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Something that's not on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, the ultimate Ri Majon\Nthat can be achieved by a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,They say it can inscribe\Nthe final miracle on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Final?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simulating the Emerald\NRi Majon of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,How would that make\NNeviril feel if she saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was I doing a Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:50.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's what that was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:58.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Aer.\N— Hey, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\NI've never seen it before myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, didn't Neviril and Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:19.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,So Neviril and Amuria did it.\NThe Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I get it! They didn't succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:31.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,So that's it. Not with Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh my! You're so thorough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,The god\NTempus Spatium is a neat freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the water's murky,\NTempus Spatium won't come near.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what Mother said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:04.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,According to her, misfortune seeps in\Nthrough dirty kitchens and bathtubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're amazing. You know so\Nmany things I've never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:11.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it best suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cleaning house\Nlike this, cooking meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was only\Ndreaming for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:23.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's so stuck on I can barely\Nscrape it off! If we had citrus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Citrus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,The acid rubs stains away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:29.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I said, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do it with me! The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.\NIt was a bust with Amuria, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:26.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know I'll work out. Come on,\NNeviril, let's do the Emerald...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:27.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll get something to wipe that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:44.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We just don't talk about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it reminds\Nyou of Amuria's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was just going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel so sorry for Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never knew Amuria personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:28.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,But to speak ill of\Nthe dead is an unforgivable sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on. I was only...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:54.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why'd you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:58.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez.\NListen, do you love Neviril or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:08.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wishing to chat just a second more\Nor hold her tight and feel her warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The kind of love where you\Ndesire her more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,I desire Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I'm with Neviril,\NI know I can fly higher than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,How'd it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since we're not about\Nto go into battle, it felt weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,When you stop feeling that way,\Nit'll mean you're really in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:42.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril was in love with Amuria.\NDo you get what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do\Nwith the Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's better in all kinds\Nof ways when you're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:03.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:19.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll happen with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:44.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:55.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because it reminds\Nyou of Amuria's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! What's wrong, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:02.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll open the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:48.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's horribly dusty in here, but Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'd rather not be in the same\Nroom with everybody, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:59.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right... you get some rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,It must be incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,With Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:39.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind who I do it with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you love Dominüra, Rimone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you do, then you'll want to kiss even\Nwhen you're not in a Simoun, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hear it's better in all\Nways when you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,All kinds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, all kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did the Powers That Be say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:16.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,That so long as the enemy's idle,\Nwe'll take a wait-and-see approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,After discovering that aerial base,\Nthey're saying to let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:25.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems an unexpected crisis\Noccurred aboard the Arcus Prima...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and everything's in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:32.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the here and now is so distracting\Nthat they're missing the big picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,If this goes on, Kyuukoku will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:41.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I may, you seem\Nto be in some kind of rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:45.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Far be it from me to presume\Nsuch things of a sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I would say that's accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NIs there some problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you feel like you were in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Run along now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:44.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria is... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whoops-a-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,You could choke in this room.\NIt's full of old junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no air circulation.\NAll that's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:28.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is useless memories, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:33.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to go.\NLet's open the door together, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,T-That hurts, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril's exhausted. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:31.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I don't think Aer\Nmeans you any harm. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to get some sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:40.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where's Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:10.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,What she said was\Nshocking, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:14.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not just Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:17.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,All this time, the rest\Nof us were avoiding it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Saying those words out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:25.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because if we did, it felt as though\Nwe'd never be able to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:28.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria was so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:33.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Always looking skyward...\NShe never seemed unsure of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:38.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, war was something\NI never thought I could handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:43.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but if she was there,\NI thought we couldn't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's how she made me feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I was afraid to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I still don't want\Nto admit it, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:54.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh, guess I'm busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind of animal is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,So funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!\NI worked really hard sewing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure, I made him a little uglier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's already met his doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, he hasn't. He's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess you could\Nsay he took after his creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to hurt Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:09.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that I felt if we were together,\Nwe could accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:10.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can you be so sure of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:16.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you never\Nexperienced utter despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I had, what good would it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:30.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Entrusting Neviril to you\Nmay have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:44.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to wait\Nfor orders from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:48.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that the enemy's idle,\Nwe must investigate that aerial base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, Aer, I leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, these two are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two are, at the moment,\NChor Tempest's top pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:06.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra, I'm not in a place\Nwhere I can team up with Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said so\Nyesterday, right? The Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,People's emotions aren't toys!\NIf you're speculating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... want to fly with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to put\NKyuukoku above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are Simoun sibyllae after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,— I knew it was futile.\N— It's not futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:26.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not futile.\NYou and I will be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their prayers were heard, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,So emotional stuff had\Nnothing to do with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:53.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not possible. The only\Nexplanation would be that Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:55.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:11.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew it. You're seeking me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:19.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can fly if you're with me.\NYou can do it if you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Am I really seeking Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:25.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:28.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I... Because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:34.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm afraid of Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:47.92,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:52.15,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:59.19,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:06.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:19.71,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:24.89,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:28.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:32.83,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:38.77,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:44.25,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.71,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:53.41,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:59.61,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.59,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:11.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to dismantle\Na Simoun, Sibylla Dominüra?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:18.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sacrosanct.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:19.97,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sacrosanct
